Product Description

Fashion hobo bag made of soft and durable PU Faux leather (Vegan leather), with anti-scratch and slightly water-resistance; With classic and modern gold hardware, side tassel, add much elegance. A beautiful, modern, and practical bag for women. Large enough for daily essentials, it can fill your mobile phone, iPad, wallet, sunglasses, and other essentials in women's bags and handbags. You can carry the women's bag as a shoulder bag, tote bag, large bag, or crossbody bag on different occasions with the short handle and the long strap.

Classic Hobo Style Bag

  • top zip closure, with 2 side zippered pockets and elegant decoration tassel, fashionable and practical for women, perfect for shopping, dating, travel, and business.
  • High-quality Faux leather, reinforced shoulder strap, and improved zipper quality.
  • Faux leather bags are shockproof and wear-resistant.
  • Removable and adjustable long shoulder strap.

See more

Structure

One Main Compartment One central zippered pocket, one interior zippered pocket, one cell phone pocket, one zippered paper napkin pocket, enough capacity to keep your daily items organized.

Material

Made of faux leather, durable handle, much more comfortable. Smooth zipper, easy to pull golden hardware, adds much elegance. Adjustable and removable long strap.

Bag Size

Medium Size: 32 x 13 x 30 (L x W x H) cm. Short handle height: 25cm, This hobo bag comes with a long removable and adjustable shoulder strap, which can be used as a women shoulder bag or hobo cross-body bag.

How are ratings calculated?
To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyses reviews to verify trustworthiness.

4.0 out of 5 stars This Bag is good for work and travelling. Very spacious bag indeed ! Lots of storage options 👌🏻
Reviewed in India on 10 April 2022
I was looking for a spacious bag to gift it to my 3 friends who are teachers. So I ordered one to check if it fits the bill. And boy ! It does a good job. It has multiple storage options for storing nick- knacks and books, iPads etc .. the only down side was the material on the exterior but considering the amount (1399/- as on 10 April 2022) we shouldn’t expect moon. It has a thin border of black which looks quite nice.I hope the chain is sturdy enough and lasts longer. The best I LOVED was a waterproof kind of material on the inside .. so just in case the water leaks out of the water bottle or oil from ur Tiffin .. likelihood of it staining stuff on the other compartment seems less … which is soo soo good I tell u. The divider flap on the inside is actually dividing the compartments into two neat spaces and not just hanging from the bottom part .. it is stitched neatly right up to the bottom part.All in all - I strongly recommend it to ppl who want spacious bag. Go for it ❤️
